templatesYaml.seoDescription: Find out which makes and models in the United States your application can connect to using Smartcar.

hero.heading: Compatible cars at a glance
hero.subheading: Find out which makes and models your application can connect to using Smartcar.

sharedContent.body: The Smartcar platform is compatible with cars across 31 brands in the United States and beyond. The following table highlights the capabilities of each make and model in the selected country.
sharedContent.body2: For more granular information regarding a specific vehicle, please use our VIN-based |+|Compatibility API@@https://smartcar.com/docs/api#compatibility-api|+|.
sharedContent.noMakeSelectedDisclaimer: Compatibility may vary by model. To determine which models are compatible, select a specific make from the drop-down menu.
sharedContent.makeSelectedDisclaimer: Compatibility may vary by trim. To determine whether a specific vehicle is compatible, please use our |+|Compatibility API@@https://smartcar.com/docs/api#compatibility-api|+|.
sharedContent.europeSelectedDisclaimer: Compatibility may vary by model. View a |+|full list@@/global/|+| of the European countries where Smartcar is available.
